sql:
SELECT users.screen_name
FROM users
JOIN tweets ON users.user_id = tweets.user_id
WHERE tweets.retweets = (
    SELECT MAX(retweets) FROM tweets
);

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM users
WHERE followers_count = (SELECT MAX(followers_count) FROM users);

external_knowledge:
- "Highly influential" and "significant following" in this context refer to verified users with at least 1000 followers;
- "Positive engagement" indicates a high sentiment score, a large number of favorites, and a substantial number of retweets;
- "Over the last year" specifically refers to the time period between January 1, 2022, and December 31, 2022.
